  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00001",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "大吹场，四龙套、四大铠、二将、申伯侯同上。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00002",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "统领雄兵，满腹经纶，声明振，神鬼皆惊，独把边疆镇。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00003",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "列国纷纷起战征，不分昼夜动刀兵。分茅列土强争胜，共图霸业立功勋。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00004",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "本爵，申伯侯，周室驾前为臣，坐守申国。只因秦楚，累累交兵，打从吾国过境。人马纷纷，扰乱百姓。幸喜两国，近已解和，吾国免受骚扰。看帅字旗，无风自动，定有军情。左右，伺候了。",
      "text_length": 85
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00005",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "探子上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00006",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "探子"
      ],
      "text": "启千岁：今有周天子，因戎狄犯境，点起烟墩，各国并不接应。周王已逃出皇城，看堪来到骊山来了。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00007",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "再探！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00008",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "探子下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00009",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "且住，适才探马报到：戎狄犯境，周王焚起烟墩，各国诸侯，道他又是与那妃子，饮酒取乐，均不发兵，以至天子蒙尘在外。本当领兵前往，怎奈昏王无道，贪恋酒色，酷害黎民；将吾妹子，贬出昭阳，打入冷宫，十分可恼。吾不免去到骊山，等候昏王到来，历数其罪，以表忠心。众将官，听吾令下：",
      "text_length": 133
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00010",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "适才探马一声禀，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00011",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "周天子他本是酒色昏君。宠褒姒不善笑烟墩火引，惹动了众诸侯带兵来临。哪知道君与妃闲把酒饮，只落得有兴来没兴回程。到如今有戎狄前来犯境，那周王无计奈又焚烟墩。众诸侯只道是又把酒饮，因此上一个个均不发兵。那昏王在国中候兵不应，无奈何他只得逃出了皇城。叫人来与爷把路引，",
      "text_length": 131
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00012",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "去到骊山等候昏君。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00013",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00014",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二马童、大将、周幽王同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00015",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "打开玉笼出彩凤，折断金锁走蛟龙。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00016",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "孤，周幽王。可恨戎狄，带兵犯上，兵困都城。是孤家焚起烟墩，指望众诸侯，前来相救。谁想他们，俱按兵不发。孤家万分无奈，连夜逃出皇城，意欲到鲁国求救。看前面，已是骊山地面，乃申伯所管，不免催马前往。",
      "text_length": 97
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00017",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "孤王催马往前走，心中恼恨各路诸侯。墩台火起不来救，险些儿性命难保留。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00018",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00019",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、二将、申伯侯同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00020",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "旌旗不住空飘扬，统领人马出朝堂。人来带路骊山上，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00021",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同转场，申伯侯下马。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00022",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "昏王到此报端详。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00023",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "申伯侯下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00024",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "君臣们急忙往前闯，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00025",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二马童、大将、周幽王同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00026",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "在马上好叫孤怒满胸膛。恨只恨小戎狄发来兵将，他要夺孤王的锦绣家邦。实指望焚烟墩调来战将，各国中发人马好救孤王。又谁知众诸侯袖手观望，倒叫那戎狄兵大肆猖狂。孤一身无辅弼难以抵挡，因此上离都城且把身藏。叫人来忙带路一齐前往，",
      "text_length": 110
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00027",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "吓！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00028",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "又只见山坡上旌旗飘扬。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00029",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "来，看前面旌旗招展，是何人的旗号？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00030",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大将"
      ],
      "text": "启万岁：那帅旗之上，写的是“申”字。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00031",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "哦哈哈呀，原来是申伯在此。此人性情耿直，颇有忠心。前番他也谏过孤家，孤将他赶出朝门，又将他妹子申后，打入冷宫。今日见面，倒觉得有些惭愧。但事已至此，只好向前见过。正是：",
      "text_length": 84
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00032",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "忠言虽逆耳，只好暂听从。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00033",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "忽听申伯在山上，倒叫孤家着了忙。忍气吞声向前闯，看他怎样对待孤王。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00034",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "龙套"
      ],
      "text": "启千岁：周王驾到！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00035",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "众将官，将旗门列开！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00036",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "耳边厢又听得人声喧嚷，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00037",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "申伯侯上，坐高台。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00038",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "骊山下又来了小周王。睁开了杀人眼朝下望，又只见他君臣狼狈仓皇。这一朝人王主成何模样，问君王驾到此所为哪桩？",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00039",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "他那里故意儿把话来讲，倒叫孤一时间面带彷徨。走向前施一礼把言奉上，尊一声申伯侯细听端详：都只为小戎狄他国犯上，逼得孤逃性命无处躲藏。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00040",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "你道那小戎狄兴兵犯上，就应该调诸侯齐动刀枪。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00041",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "孤也曾焚烟墩调选兵将，又谁知众诸侯他不救孤王。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00042",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "说什么众诸侯不来救你，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00043",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "这也是你当初做事全非：曾记得你那年得了褒姒，你因她不善笑设计胡为。那时间你命人把烟墩焚起，众诸侯率甲兵前去对敌。到台下来观看并无一骑，乃是你同褒姒饮酒欢娱。只落得一个个垂头丧气，各诸侯也只好携鼓卷旗。那褒姒她那时笑容可掬，乐得你小昏王颠倒昏迷。到如今你又将烟墩焚起，众诸侯他岂肯再把兵提？",
      "text_length": 144
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00044",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "那时间是孤家太无理，到如今好叫孤无有话提。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00045",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "已往之事，提他则甚？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00046",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "我且问你，你意欲何往？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00047",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "孤想鲁国，与孤乃是弟兄之国，孤意欲到那里搬兵，杀退戎狄，孤再回国复位。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00048",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "你这昏王，既经出了朝廷，只恐你不能归国了！",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00049",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "怎见得？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00050",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "你且听道：自盘古以至三皇，传位于尧舜，天下大治。为君之道，必以道德安邦，以仁义定国。爱民如子，厚待朝臣，去谗远色，威服四夷。夏禹商汤，即是明灯。彼等亡天下之君，皆以荒淫酒色，酷害忠良。夏桀王宠爱妹嬉，造下酒池、肉林，屈害忠臣，关龙逢因谏君而死，成汤放桀于南巢；商王传流四百年，以至殷纣，也是荒淫无度，宠爱妲己，造虿盆、炮烙之惨刑，忠臣梅柏、赵启，俱遭荼毒，比干丞相，挖心而亡。后来武王伐纣，那纣王，只落得焚死在摘星楼。你这昏王，不知遵循祖宗训诏，竟敢任意荒淫。要想闯过此界，只怕你不能得够了！",
      "text_length": 246
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00051",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "自古帝王定家邦，全仗仁义布朝堂。道德休明政治讲，圣神文武定边疆。朝廷专重忠良将，惠爱黎民在四方。前朝亡国有榜样，皆只为贪酒色屈害忠良！",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00052",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "这些话儿休言讲，细听孤王说端详：你妹子本是昭阳院，难道说你不看在亲戚情肠？",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00053",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "呀呀呀呸！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00054",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "说什么看在了亲戚情肠，提起了亲戚事我怒满胸膛。我妹子为正宫身犯何罪，打入了冷宫中所为哪桩？宠爱那淫褒姒昭阳来掌，宠妾灭妻罪非常。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00055",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "周幽王"
      ],
      "text": "孤把好言对你讲，反把孤王骂一场。你今不把孤来放，欺君压上骂名扬。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01024007_e00056",
      "play_id": "01024007",
      "scene_id": "01024007_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "申伯侯"
      ],
      "text": "昏王说话不思想，申伯侯本是大忠良。事到头来想一想，你本是人面兽心肠。叫人来将昏王一齐来绑，管叫你君臣们无有下场！",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
